      "author": "yasd251",
      "description": "# What's new\r\n  - Sounds now load from the plugin assets/ folder accessible from the plugin settings! You can now add in your own sound completion effects by dropping in a .mp3 or .wav file. (3 default sounds are pre-installed with the plugin: calm bell, pop, ting)\r\n  - Sounds now trigger on keyboard shortcuts (i.e ⌘+L), not just mouse clicks!\r\n  - Animation appears strictly at the checkbox location, not at random locations\r\n\r\n  Bug fixes\r\n  - Fixed large red/green squares appearing with confetti animation",
